# graphify knowledge graph: track the shareable graph + human report only.
# The HTML viz is regenerable from graph.json; cache/, cost.json, manifest.json,
# and the .graphify_* dotfiles are per-clone local state.
graphify-out/*
!graphify-out/graph.json
!graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md
